ZH: 癌细胞是身体内的恶性细胞。
EN: Cancer cells are malignant cells in the body.

ZH: 癌细胞可以通过分裂和生长扩散。
EN: Cancer cells can spread through division and growth.

ZH: 无法控制的癌细胞会造成严重的健康问题。
EN: Uncontrolled cancer cells can cause serious health problems.

ZH: 癌细胞会侵入周围的组织并破坏正常功能。
EN: Cancer cells can invade surrounding tissues and disrupt normal functions.

ZH: 化疗的目标是消灭体内的癌细胞。
EN: The goal of chemotherapy is to eliminate cancer cells in the body.

ZH: 癌细胞具有很高的生存能力。
EN: Cancer cells have a high level of survivability.

ZH: 医生会预估癌细胞的扩散程度。
EN: Doctors will estimate the extent of cancer cell spread.

ZH: 癌细胞的检测可以通过生物标志物来进行。
EN: Testing for cancer cells can be done through biomarkers.

ZH: 放疗可以用来减少癌细胞的数量。
EN: Radiation therapy can be used to reduce the number of cancer cells.

ZH: 肿瘤的生长速度与癌细胞的活跃程度有关。
EN: The growth rate of tumors is related to the activity of cancer cells.

ZH: 癌细胞的变异使其更难被免疫系统识别。
EN: The mutation of cancer cells makes them more difficult to be recognized by the immune system.

ZH: 营养不良可能导致癌细胞的生长。
EN: Malnutrition may lead to the growth of cancer cells.

ZH: 癌细胞的治疗需要根据具体情况来制定。
EN: Treatment for cancer cells needs to be tailored to individual cases.

ZH: 癌细胞的首要目标是扩散和侵入其他组织。
EN: The primary goal of cancer cells is to spread and invade other tissues.

ZH: 免疫疗法可以用来增强免疫系统对癌细胞的攻击性。
EN: Immunotherapy can be used to enhance the immune system's attack on cancer cells.

ZH: 了解癌细胞的生长机制对治疗至关重要。
EN: Understanding the growth mechanism of cancer cells is crucial for treatment.

ZH: 癌细胞的基因突变会影响其生长和传播。
EN: Genetic mutations in cancer cells can affect their growth and spread.

ZH: 干细胞疗法可能被用来对抗治疗难度大的癌细胞。
EN: Stem cell therapy may be used to combat treatment-resistant cancer cells.

ZH: 手术可以切除体内的癌细胞。
EN: Surgery can remove cancer cells from the body.
